&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://wiki.bigledger.com/applets/chart-of-account-applet/" &gt;Chart of Account Applet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Account mapping&lt;/li&gt;
